                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>ari</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Getae Severo <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> divi Septi<lb break="no" n="3"/>mi Severi Pii Pertinacis <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Arabici Adiabenici <expan><abbr>Parthi</abbr><ex>ci</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>aximi</ex></expan> pacatoris orbis <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>et <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> Aurelii Antonini <expan><abbr>imper</abbr><ex>atoris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>frat</abbr><ex>ri</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>res <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ublica</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Tuccit</abbr><ex>anorum</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>atum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecreto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurionum</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Das Stück ist heute verschollen. Datierung: nach dem 4. Februar (Tod d. Severus) und vor dem 19. oder 26. Dezember (Ermordung Getas).</p>
